    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Day by day, I tried to stop this song."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What is it? There must be something wrong..."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh! This life is just a hopelessness!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Always searching, but tasting emptiness."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is an answer: a wonderful Person!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s Jesus the Lord; He’s God’s beloved Son!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This wonderful Person is now your solution."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just take and receive Him; He’s God’s Firstborn Son!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All day long you play the “same ole song”:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Good morning”, “How are you?”, “No, there is nothing wrong.”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You’re swept by the world of deceptive vanity,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "A tide looking good, but it’s void of reality."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just call “Oh Lord Jesus”: the truth you’re confessing"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That God raised this Jesus from among the dead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your heart this believing, just call to receive Him."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s Jesus the Savior, your great salvation."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You’re conformed to unreality,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Trapped in a wheel of human anxiety."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You are caught, you’re in the web already."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You’re spun to this song: you’re just the spider’s prey."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus crushed the devil and overcame evil."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That kingdom He leveled and destroyed the devil."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He will free you from sin, from death, world and Satan."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just call “Oh Lord Jesus” and He will enter in."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life is a song as a time hour glass,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Sand by sand, my friend it cannot last."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You’re born, you live, and eventually you die."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Friend, you can’t change it, no need to even try."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There is a new song, a wonderful Person!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s Jesus the Lord, He’s God’s beloved Son!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This wonderful Person is now your solution!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just take and receive Him; He’s God’s Firstborn Son!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    }
